more advanced crops. Your population needs housing, clean water, electricity, healthcare, and household goods. Keep them happy and healthy, and they will reward you with Unity, a resource that lets you speed up construction, enact powerful edicts, and claim resources on the world map. Neglect waste management or let pollution build up, and diseases will spread.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore, trade, and become self-sufficient</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594320/extras/7801ca7de3b328c4747053281be93ea2.poster.avif?t=1773870727\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594320/extras/7801ca7de3b328c4747053281be93ea2.webm?t=1773870727\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594320/extras/7801ca7de3b328c4747053281be93ea2.mp4?t=1773870727\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Send your ship out to explore the world map. Discover new islands with resources to import, refugees to rescue, and allied settlements to trade with. Establish shipping contracts for recurring exchanges, or negotiate quick trades when you need something fast. Your ultimate goal is full self-sufficiency: launch rockets, build a space station, and mine asteroids for rare resources that make your colony independent indefinitely.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your tools</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594320/extras/273cba9c448e54ae10862a010af8bebb.poster.avif?t=1773870727\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1594320/extras/273cba9c448e54ae10862a010af8bebb.webm?